```
include(
    "graphql", "user", "call", "chat", "feed",
    "notification", "product", "tracking", "adreward",
    "scheduler", "grouptalk", "domain", "protobuf"
)
```

**Dependency Graph**:
- `graphql` тЖТ depends on `domain`, `protobuf` (client to all services)
- `user`, `call`, `chat`, etc. тЖТ depend on `domain`, `protobuf`
- `domain` тЖТ independent (entities & repositories)
- `protobuf` тЖТ independent (generated from .proto files)

**Key Commands**:
```bash
./gradlew clean build -x test              # Full build
./gradlew :user:build -x test              # Build specific module
./gradlew :protobuf:clean :protobuf:build  # Regenerate gRPC stubs
./gradlew :domain:compileKotlin            # Compile entities only
```

